data.title: Excellent thai food in downtown Vancouver
data.text:
This great food cart is in the heart of one of the great areas of downtown Vancouver.  The pot stickers are great. The pad thai never has much chicken,  but you can ask for more. The yakisoba is great.  Spring rolls are delicious. 

Order and then take a walk while your food is cooked. :)

data.title: Thai To Go
data.text:
Thai food to go!  Or... sit in the taproom (great beer, wish I could remember their name)! next to it.  They welcome the local restaurant food in their courtyard or inside seating if you buy a beverage from them.  Or take your food across the street to the Thirsty Sasquatch... a nice whisky bar with the occasional live band.

Esan has freshly made food, generous portions and is Yummy! 

My favorite is Pineapple Fried Rice medium spicy.
